Introducing
Open WebUI
The self-hosted AI interface.
Open WebUI is the platform for running AI on your own terms. Connect to any model—local or
 cloud. Extend with Python. Share what you build with 329K others. 270 million downloads and growing.
Learn more
Built
for you
A home for AI.
Every model, every conversation, every tool—in one place. Connect to Ollama, OpenAI, Anthropic,
 or anything compatible. Run locally, in the cloud, or both. Data stays exactly where it belongs.
Documentation
The community
platform
329,161 members sharing what they've built.
Prompts, models, tools, functions, discussions and reviews—created by the community, available
 to everyone. Browse, install, contribute. Everything at openwebui.com.
Explore the community
Full
toolkit
Everything AI offers. Available now.
Voice, vision, retrieval, generation, search. Extend with Python. Ready from day one.
Prompts
Shared by the community
Models
Any persona, any configuration
Tools
RAG, search, execution

Python pipelines
Built for
scale
AI for every organization.
From startups to global enterprises. SSO, RBAC, audit logs built for regulated industries. One
 platform. Complete control. No compromises.
Talk to our team
Our
mission
Open WebUI is being built so everyone can run AI for themselves.
Not rent it. Not depend on it. Own it. Self-sufficient, adaptable, and ready for wherever
 humanity goes—from a laptop to the stars.
